author: SUJEWAN VIJAYAKUMAR
text:
The facilities are clean, well-maintained, and equipped with modern machines. The staff is incredibly friendly and always ready to assist. Highly recommend this gym to anyone looking for a convenient and welcoming fitness environment!

Both Armaan and Russ are exceptional personal trainers! Their knowledge, professionalism, and dedication to helping clients achieve their fitness goals are truly commendable. I've seen significant progress in my fitness journey thanks to their guidance and support. Highly recommend booking sessions with either of them!

author: Clement Santhanasamy
text: Great place to have a good fitness. Gym with good and new and basic equipment which is necessary to workout, if you plan to get into boxing, they do provide personal sessions for it and our friend Ahmeed is such a wonderful person to work with. Iâ€™ve personally have sessions with him and I loved his workout routine. Not forgetting our brother Russ as well who is a bodybuilder himself who can also help to get yourself into either bodybuilding or into fitness as well. Do check out if youâ€™re up to guys! Iâ€™m really enjoying working out with them. God bless them for guiding me all this while and looking forward for more time together with them.

author: Lance Allen
text:
I highly recommend this newly opened Anytime Fitness at Upper Changi with amazing facilities and equipments ranging from free weights, weight machines and cardio machines to meet your fitness needs.

The staff are very friendly and welcoming which is what you need in a gym. The gym manager, Russ, helped me when I was using an equipment wrongly and made sure I used it properly to ensure my safety. He has also shared his knowledge with me from years of experience in the gym in order to improve on how I can be more effective with my workouts.

author: Cider Mint
text: Excellent gym - clean, with all the equipment and machines you need for a great workout. Vibe there is friendly too! The PT Rus is experienced and knowledgeable. Iâ€™ve lost 15kg thanks to him! If you want to see results heâ€™s the guy to look for!

author: Arc T
text: This Brand new Anytime Fitness has got to be on of the best I have been to so far. Well maintained equipment and very good service. Mr Armaan, one of the employees there, provides excellent service and is also a really good personal instructor. He is  helping  me in achieving my body goals for 2024 and right now itâ€™s going really well so far ðŸ˜Ž

author: Danial Shah
text: Love this gym! The staff is super friendly and helpful, and the equipment is top-notch. It's always clean, which I really appreciate. If you're looking for a gym with a welcoming atmosphere and convenient amenities, this is definitely the place to be.

author: Juventus Jeganathan
text: My go-to outlet simply because it has all the basic equipments that you would need and no crowd. Russ is a solid lad who's always quick to share tips and advice on how to perform exercises and offers great PT sessions as well. Would highly recommend him for your PT needs.

author: Spartan Dan
text:
I came in a time when the gym is quite empty. Everything is relatively new. Very clean and good atmosphere.
One squat rack with in built deadlift platform.
Another squat rack..
A few machines with loaded plates as well. And bodyweight area for functional exercises.
Decent and good enough for a quick workout.
This gym only can get a 4 star as I believe the toilet is quite a distance to walk if I need to urgently rush, jialat.
And parking lot is quite pricey so for bikers can park at the private estate area but at your own risk lor.

author: Aaron Philip
text:
AF Upp Changi is a hidden gem. A well organised gym with good ambience.

Russ is a knowledgeable trainer there with many years of training experience under his belt. A friendly giant with awesome personality, he's able to customise a training plan accordingly to meet your fitness goals at whichever stage of life you are at.

Not just planning, but having a good understanding of the inner human dynamics, emotions, motivation, will power etc is able to journey through with you to achieve your goals.

author: Xavier Tei
text: Excellent gym. Clean and tidy. I came from another Anytime Fitness and I love it here. Staff are friendly and lovely. They welcome everyone from any other gym here. I love it here.

author: Charm
text: Small but compact and well equipped gym for most of your basic gym needs, and staff are very friendly and ready to assist. Toilets are located outside but within the building compound as well.

author: Yong Lum
text: Embarking on a fitness journey with PT Russ. Russ is friendly and provides good professional guidance. The gym is new and clean. Time for workout!

author: A S
text:
So glad this new outlet is conveniently located near my place. The staff are friendly and welcoming so thatâ€™s a huge plus.
Good to see that they hired experienced and knowledgeable trainers in the gym as well!

author: Mikhail Shah
text: Great gym, friendly staff, not too crowded. Has pretty much whatever you need to get a any kind of workout in. Highly recommend!

author: Farah Hayati
text: Great gym! Plus, the trainers are friendly and are happy to help with the use of equipment!

author: Yugendrann Pannir Selvam
text: Best gym in the area! Had an amazing PT session with Armaan! Hit him up for a well guided PT session!
